==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Koel
<hw>Ko"el</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Native name in
India.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of several species of
cuckoos of the genus <gen>Eudynamys</gen>, found in India, the East
Indies, and Australia. They deposit their eggs in the nests of other
birds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Koellia</ent>⟦br⟧
